{"tid":2252764,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"小熊插畫麵包","createTime":"2020-10-21T16:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T17:30:57.000Z","uid":276969,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c59f8e3ba2abf5c2d071f9665bd83dc3f49b40","tid":2252764,"uid":276969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"今天想要介紹一款我家小朋友都很喜歡的可愛小熊插畫麵包。<br />\n做小熊插畫麵包，是因為小女兒很喜歡一個小熊公仔，叫小美，女兒想讓我做一個小熊麵包給她做早餐。做這款插畫麵包要花蠻多時間的，但小朋友第二天早上起來看到小熊麵包驚喜得開心大叫，然後大口大口吃早餐的時候, 再累都覺得是值得的。<br />\n做法和食譜可在這裡找到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=22f42c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXQH5PdJroy7_AdIGp0-VBw</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SXx8Em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SXx8Em.jpg&h=3e27fa39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EkAohlebDiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEkAohlebDiw&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=8444c934\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EkAohlebDiw</a>"},{"pid":"c6d9170ba96f02188cb73823955a20a7c343f4e3","tid":2252764,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cd535c5320c4a8c5bebe2b15b12d109c0a6d2d","tid":2252764,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c2fdd80497db55fe301a31236a91b9202a3a259","tid":2252764,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i